## âœ… 3. **Deploy to Streamlit Cloud**

1. Go to [Streamlit Cloud](https://streamlit.io/cloud).
2. Click **"Deploy an app"**.
3. Connect to your GitHub repo.
4. Select:
   - Repo: `color-detection-app`
   - Branch: `main`
   - Main file: `app.py`
5. Click **Deploy**.

Your app will go live at:  
`https://<your-username>-color-detection-app.streamlit.app`

